# Quirks — {{app_slug}}

This file accumulates short notes about flaky or unexpected behavior observed during `/qa` runs against the `{{app_slug}}` app. The orchestrator surfaces relevant entries before running flows that touch the same area.

One file per app: `.maestro/qa/quirks/{{app_slug}}.md`. Entries are append-only across runs; the installer never rewrites this file once created.

Format per entry:

```
## <flow_id> — <one-line title>

- Date: <YYYY-MM-DD>
- Status: <observed | mitigated | resolved>
- Note: <one or two sentences>
```

Do not delete this file. The installer regenerates the orchestrator and per-app skills, but it preserves quirk entries across runs.
